Package: snpsettest
Title: A set-based association test using GWAS summary statistics for complex-traits
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jaehyun",
           family = "Joo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jaehyunjoo@outlook.com")
Description: The goal of 'snpsettest' is to provide simple tools to compute
             SNP-set level p-values using GWAS summary statistics. The primary
             application of this package is gene-based tests.
